org.cfpm.factbaseExtension
Class FactBaseExtension

java.lang.Object
  org.nlogo.api.DefaultClassManager
      org.cfpm.factbaseExtension.FactBaseExtension
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.nlogo.api.ClassManager, scala.ScalaObject
public class FactBaseExtension
extends org.nlogo.api.DefaultClassManager

This is the main class of the factbase extension. It defines all primitives for use in NetLogo. It also provides some useful functionality for interfacing NetLogo and Java, to be used by the classes implementing the different primitives.

Author:
Ruth Meyer

load

public void load(org.nlogo.api.PrimitiveManager primManager)
          throws org.nlogo.api.ExtensionException
Specifies the primitives available for the factbase extension. This method is called each time a model using the extension is compiled in NetLogo.
